      "instruction": "<p>To build, spread the <strong>cranberry mayo </strong>evenly between the <strong>ciabatta bases</strong> and top with your <strong>crispy onions</strong>, <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>bacon</strong>, <strong>sliced tomato</strong>, <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>onion marmalade </strong>and <strong>ciabatta lids</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>cheesy garlic wedges </strong>and <strong>remaining shredded lettuce </strong>to the side</p><p>Top the shredded lettuce with the <strong>diced tomato</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and enjoy!</p>",
